## What is this?

This is a customizable application built on three.js that allows users to design an interior space such as a home or apartment. Below are screenshots from our Example App.

## Features

- **2D Floorplan Editor** - Create and edit floor plans interactively
- **3D Visualization** - View and modify your design in real-time 3D
- **Item Placement** - Add and arrange furniture and items in your space
- **Customizable** - Built as a modular library for easy integration

